Kakamega County Senator Cleophas Malala Has Been Suspended From The Membership Of ANC Party With Immediate Effect Pending Appearance Before The Party’s National Disciplinary Committee To Explain Why He Should Not Be Expelled For Flouting The Party Constitution. Malala Is Accused of Openly Campaigning for ODM Candidate Bernard Imran Okoth, In The Just Concluded Kibra Constituency By Election, Whereas ANC Had Fielded Eliud Owalo As The Party’s Flag Bearer.